生突破。男子肝癌晚期只打一针重获新生！费用或仅需 3 万"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-807e3f5a08bf1ce72a850d066c88d3be_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "311 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890066432747860802"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIo43assLG0Id9EAMaCTExNDI2Mjc3MyDpjqm/BjAAOIUBQANyEzE4OTAwNjY0MzI3NDc4NjA4MDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1743495155.581265", "card_id": "Q_1890344067877011522", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "24-25 赛季 NBA 常规赛火箭 98:104 湖人，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d0daf220ba59218fa0e1920908c5dc2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "196 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890344067877011522"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIo43assLG0Id9EAMaCTExNDI3NDA1OSD6k62/BjAAOERABHITMTg5MDM0NDA2Nzg3NzAxMTUyMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1743495155.581559", "card_id": "Q_1890326773549462446", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "张国荣去世 22 周年，你对「哥哥」有哪些记忆？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 1 日是张国荣逝世 22 周年，唐鹤德在社交平台分享了张国荣旧照，并写道：「谁能代替你地位 ❤️」 哥哥想你了 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b8eecd90cdfe6010d59da04c21a2b40f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "167 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "t